replace \x093C  

always \x0915\x093C\x094D 4-5-13 #"ka with nukhta"
always \x0916\x093C\x094D 4-5-46 #"kha with nukhta"
always \x0917\x093C\x094D 4-5-1245 #"ga with nukhta"
